# AKIKO Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AKIKO runs fully without any of these keys.
# All three are OPTIONAL — each unlocks additional capabilities.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Optional: Anthropic API key — enables Meta-Learning loop (Page 2)
# Get a free key at: https://console.anthropic.com/
# Without this key: all statistical prediction features still work normally.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional: Football-Data.org API key — unlocks more competitions & higher rate limits
# Free tier (no key): top-5 leagues, 10 requests/min — works out of the box.
# Free key available at: https://www.football-data.org/client/register
# FOOTBALL_DATA_API_KEY=

# Optional: The Odds API key — enables live Pinnacle market_implied component
# Without this key: market_implied weight is redistributed to real-data components.
# Free tier: 500 requests/month at https://the-odds-api.com/
# ODDS_API_KEY=

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These APIs need NO key and are always active:
#   OpenLigaDB    — https://api.openligadb.de       (Bundesliga, free forever)
#   TheSportsDB   — https://www.thesportsdb.com     (all leagues, free tier)
#   Open-Meteo    — https://api.open-meteo.com      (weather, free forever)
#   Understat     — https://understat.com            (xG, public HTML)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
